title: Galle Face protest: protestors moving towards Presidential Secretariat
body_lines: COLOMBO (News 1st); A protest is currently underway with the participation of a large number of people at Galle Face, Colombo.
News 1st Correspondents stated that a large number of people including professionals and youth are participating in the protest, which is hoping to draw massive crowds.
